# Development Preferences
# -----------------------
# - Use clean, readable code and good naming
# - Keep logic modular and maintainable
# - Use comments to explain tricky or important logic
# - Use requestAnimationFrame for the game loop
# - Use DOM elements for entities (divs with classes)
# - Use getBoundingClientRect() for collision detection
# - Keep keyboard + touch controls unified
# - Make all movement time-based and responsive to container size
# - Avoid global sprawl; group related logic

